OL,3,CJersey taxi drivers call on government
OL,4,Cto crack down on unlicensed vehicles
OL,6,FTaxi drivers and an independent think-
OL,7,Ftank in Jersey are calling for the
OL,8,Fisland's taxi regulation to be made
OL,9,Fstricter amid fears over a rise in
OL,10,Funlicensed taxi drivers.
OL,12,FJersey's taxi regulation is currently
OL,13,Finformed by the Motor Traffic (Jersey)
OL,14,FLaw 1935 which defines what can be
OL,15,Fclassed as a taxi as well as the
OL,16,Fnumber of licensed taxis that are
OL,17,Fallowed to operate on the island.
OL,19,FThere is, however, no limit on the
OL,20,Fnumber of people licensed to drive
OL,21,Ftaxis.
