OL,3,CJersey taxi drivers call on government
OL,4,Cto crack down on unlicensed vehicles
OL,6,FThe law also gives the island's
OL,7,Fgovernment extensive powers to impose
OL,8,Fstrict conditions on issuing licences
OL,9,Ffor vehicles and drivers.
OL,11,FThe number of licensed taxi drivers in
OL,12,FJersey has dropped by a quarter over
OL,13,Fthe last decade with a larger number
OL,14,Fof unlicensed and often uninsured
OL,15,Fdrivers offering people lifts for
OL,16,Fmoney.
