OL,3,CJersey taxi drivers call on government
OL,4,Cto crack down on unlicensed vehicles
OL,6,FSir Mark Boleat from Policy Centre
OL,7,FJersey praised open discussion about
OL,8,Fthe industry's future on the island in
OL,9,Fa meeting featuring members of Policy
OL,10,FCentre Jersey's Advisory Council
OL,11,Falongside business and government
OL,12,Frepresentatives on 26 July.
OL,14,FHowever, he says more needs to be done
OL,15,Fto address concerns from customers,
OL,16,Ftaxi drivers and the government on
OL,17,Fregulation.
