OL,6,FSir Mark told ITV News: "We think the
OL,7,Fmeeting went really well. What the
OL,8,FPolicy Centre is seeking to do is to
OL,9,Fhave good quality discussion on public
OL,10,Fissues, no preconceived answers, no
OL,11,Fdecisions at the end but the issues
OL,12,Fbeing raised and we think everyone
OL,13,Fwent away with a better understanding
OL,14,Fof what the issues are."
