OL,4,Cto crack down on unlicensed vehicles
OL,6,FWhen asked about what specific
OL,7,Fconcerns different groups involved in
OL,8,Fthe discussion expressed, Sir Mark
OL,9,Fsaid: "The concerns that the Jersey
OL,10,Fpublic has about the cost and
OL,11,Favailability of taxis. The concerns
OL,12,Fthat taxi drivers have about the
OL,13,Fexistence of Jersey Lifts.
OL,15,F"The reality is that Jersey Lifts
OL,16,Fexists because the regulatory system
OL,17,Fhas removed the ability to have a
OL,18,Fnormal minicab service."
