OL,3,CJersey taxi drivers call on government
OL,4,Cto crack down on unlicensed vehicles
OL,6,FHe added: "The effect is that you have
OL,7,Fthis huge Jersey Lifts operation which
OL,8,Fnaturally the taxi drivers don't like."
OL,10,FJersey Lifts is an informal taxi
OL,11,Fservice that is unregulated, although
OL,12,Fnot illegal.
OL,14,FIt has a Facebook page with over
OL,15,F30,000 followers.
OL,17,FThe Jersey Taxi Drivers Association
OL,18,Fruns the Jersey Taxi App which is
OL,19,Fwidely used on the island.
