OL,3,CJersey taxi drivers call on government
OL,4,Cto crack down on unlicensed vehicles
OL,6,FRyde is a new taxi app in Jersey which
OL,7,Fprovides a similar service to Uber,
OL,8,Fwhich does not operate on the island.
OL,10,FTaxi driver Eric Mahe says the rise of
OL,11,Funlicensed taxis on the island puts
OL,12,Fpeople at risk.
OL,14,FMr Mahe told ITV News: "I think it's
OL,15,Falways been said that there are taxi
OL,16,Fdrivers and people who drive taxis so
OL,17,Fknowing how to do the job, dealing
OL,18,Fwith any confrontation, to deal with
OL,19,Ffinances.
