OL,3,CJersey taxi drivers call on government
OL,4,Cto crack down on unlicensed vehicles
OL,6,F"Everybody should be able to do that.
OL,7,FYou can't just be able to jump in a
OL,8,Fcar and do that without some sort of
OL,9,Fhelp."
OL,11,FUnlicensed drivers can be fined up to
OL,12,F#10,000 by law but they are rarely
OL,13,Fprosecuted in Jersey.
OL,15,FCon Andy Jehan, Jersey's
OL,16,FInfrastructure Minister, says more
OL,17,Fneeds to be done to tackle unlicensed
OL,18,Ftaxis and bring about more
OL,19,Fprosecutions.
