OL,3,CJersey taxi drivers call on government
OL,4,Cto crack down on unlicensed vehicles
OL,6,FHe said: "I think we do need to change
OL,7,Fthe regulation to make it easier for
OL,8,Fthe police to prosecute Jersey Lifts.
OL,10,F"We're worried about the safety and
OL,11,Fsecurity of people who are using that
OL,12,Fservice. And we're also looking at the
OL,13,Ftaxi drivers themselves and
OL,14,Fintroducing mystery shoppers.
OL,16,F"Most of the taxi drivers do a great
OL,17,Fjob but we want them to be ambassadors
OL,18,Ffor the island so we want to encourage
OL,19,Fthem a bit more."
